description: Sublattices of index n in generic 12-dimensional lattice.
references: M. Baake, "Solution of coincidence problem...", in R. V. Moody, ed., Math. of Long-Range Aperiodic Order, Kluwer 1997, pp. 9-44.
links: Index entries for sequences related to sublattices
formula: f(Q, n)=Sum d*f(Q-1, d), d|n; here Q=12.Multiplicative with a(p^e) = product (p^(e+k)-1)/(p^k-1), k=1..11.Dirichlet g.f. product_{k=0..Q-1} zeta(s-k).
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_.
extensions: Offset set to 1. - R. J. Mathar, Apr 01 2011
